         <abstract id="aspace_9f1f9dc2844ca076195360a360cbd343">The records consist of letters, maps, scrapbooks, works of art, and other assorted objects given to the president of Yale University as gifts. Included are gifts received from the president of Wuhan University in the People's Republic of China, Moscow State University, Famille Aycardi Archives, and the American Association of Teachers of Spanish and Portuguese.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_f452813da71871a1fab40d4432043d81">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 2-A (YRG 2-A), Records of the Yale president's office.</p>  
      </odd>
